title: Hawks Stay Hot with Sweep of Spartans
text:
Hawks Stay Hot with Sweep of Spartans 
By Zach Schneider October 12, 2015 Updated Oct 12, 2015 at 10:48 PM CDT 
Superior, WI (NNCNOW.com) --- The Hermantown volleyball team swept Superior 3-0 on Monday night, meaning the Hawks have now won 18 of their past 19 matches this 2015 season. 
The Hawks' winning ways have come after a three-match losing streak in early September, and the team is now (20-4) overall this season.
